1
00:01:24,789 --> 00:01:25,510
Xia.

2
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:28,660
You are even more beautiful
than I imagined.

3
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:31,200
Sister.

4
00:01:33,229 --> 00:01:34,430
I'm a little nervous.

5
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:36,680
Don't be nervous.

6
00:01:37,150 --> 00:01:38,710
I will always be with you.

7
00:01:39,590 --> 00:01:40,720
Come, come sit down.

8
00:01:53,789 --> 00:01:54,840
Mom left this.

9
00:01:56,710 --> 00:01:59,640
She said on your wedding day,

10
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:02,490
I should put these earrings on you.

11
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:03,680
She will see it.

12
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:22,870
All right,

13
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:24,590
my lovely bride,

14
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:26,520
you're flawless.

15
00:02:27,630 --> 00:02:28,400
Let's go.

16
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,150
Go.

17
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:34,750
Go.

18
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:35,590
Go.

19
00:03:54,310 --> 00:03:55,910
We've had her under control.

20
00:03:56,030 --> 00:03:56,840
But...

21
00:03:57,870 --> 00:03:59,670
there's another woman with her.

22
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,890
Leave the woman in the room.

23
00:04:02,590 --> 00:04:03,630
I only want Su Xia.

24
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,280
Yes, understood.

25
00:04:44,070 --> 00:04:44,950
You're awake.

26
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:46,560
Xiao Qi.

27
00:04:49,630 --> 00:04:50,390
Why?

28
00:04:50,870 --> 00:04:51,930
What are you doing?

29
00:04:52,310 --> 00:04:54,970
You look really beautiful
in the wedding dress.

30
00:04:55,950 --> 00:04:56,750
Such a pity.

31
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:00,380
The countdown's ticking.

32
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,560
This button in my hand

33
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:07,450
can electrify the entire cage instantly.

34
00:05:08,870 --> 00:05:11,200
Or we can wait
for the countdown to finish.

35
00:05:12,310 --> 00:05:14,440
Do you think Lu Fan will make it in time?

36
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:18,000
Why?

37
00:05:18,190 --> 00:05:19,160
Why?

38
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:29,750
Xiao Qi! Xiao Qi!

39
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:41,220
Fan, I checked the surveillance.

40
00:05:41,630 --> 00:05:43,360
Su Xia was taken away by Xiao Qi.

41
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:44,800
Fan, don't go looking for her.

42
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,200
Xiao Qi won't hurt Su Xia.

43
00:05:46,430 --> 00:05:47,560
His target is you.

44
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:50,000
Listen, I'll go find Su Xia.

45
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,159
You wait here.

46
00:05:51,190 --> 00:05:52,720
I will find my bride myself.

47
00:05:58,950 --> 00:05:59,600
Su Xia.

48
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:01,160
Su Xia!

49
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:03,160
Don't come closer! It's dangerous!

50
00:06:05,750 --> 00:06:06,480
You're here.

51
00:06:12,270 --> 00:06:13,160
Give it to me.

52
00:06:15,630 --> 00:06:16,270
Okay.

53
00:06:17,750 --> 00:06:18,480
No problem.

54
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:21,180
I can give it to you.

55
00:06:23,070 --> 00:06:23,800
Kneel

56
00:06:24,750 --> 00:06:25,390
and beg me.

57
00:06:26,270 --> 00:06:26,920
Kneel!

58
00:06:32,190 --> 00:06:33,040
Lu Fan.

59
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:52,720
Kill me.

60
00:06:54,310 --> 00:06:56,070
If you stab me in the heart,

61
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,630
my hand might slip,

62
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:59,370
and she'll be all yours.

63
00:07:01,270 --> 00:07:01,950
Do it.

64
00:07:01,950 --> 00:07:03,480
Lu Fan, don't listen to him.

65
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:05,870
Do it!

66
00:07:06,870 --> 00:07:08,190
Do it, you coward!

67
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:16,390
Come on!

68
00:07:25,830 --> 00:07:28,270
Let go! Let go! Let go!

69
00:07:30,070 --> 00:07:33,270
Lu Fan, let go! Let go!

70
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,040
You two can leave.

71
00:07:59,950 --> 00:08:00,750
Su Xia.

72
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:05,160
I won't appear in your life anymore.

73
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:09,310
Let's go.

74
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,240
Su Xia.

75
00:08:16,950 --> 00:08:17,950
Without me,

76
00:08:20,430 --> 00:08:21,890
you must live in the light.

77
00:08:57,550 --> 00:08:58,720
What are you going to say to her?

78
00:08:58,720 --> 00:08:59,910
"Sorry, I lied to you.

79
00:08:59,910 --> 00:09:00,750
This is just a setup.

80
00:09:00,750 --> 00:09:02,080
I'm here to destroy you."

81
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:04,210
Or you just can't bear to part with her?

82
00:09:11,630 --> 00:09:12,320
Have you forgotten how we survived

83
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:13,790
these years?

84
00:09:15,510 --> 00:09:16,270
Have you forgotten how the Lu family

85
00:09:16,270 --> 00:09:17,630
forced our two families to death

86
00:09:17,630 --> 00:09:18,840
and ruined our lives?

87
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:40,000
What is your name?

88
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:41,670
My name is Su Xia.

89
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:43,320
My name is Xiao Qi.

90
00:11:13,910 --> 00:11:14,670
Xiao Qi.

91
00:11:16,600 --> 00:11:17,600
You were once

92
00:11:19,270 --> 00:11:21,120
the light in my life.

93
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:24,670
You held my hand

94
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:28,450
and pulled me out of the abyss
time and time again.

95
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:36,000
But I couldn't hold onto you.

96
00:11:45,750 --> 00:11:48,480
Since you chose to free yourself this way,

97
00:11:50,030 --> 00:11:51,360
may you

98
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:55,270
find freedom

99
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:57,000
and happiness

100
00:11:58,750 --> 00:11:59,440
in the afterlife.
